          "content_hash": "a6a2f124523fa213",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "1. 学术taste非常棒, 教职第一年paper就拿了neurips主会oral和workshop awards, 10多篇尾作, 每个学生居然只有一篇代表作 (RAGEN, VAGEN, ENACT, MindCube, Theory of Space)"
